---
import Layout from '~/layouts/LandingLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Customer Care - Blood Group Detection & Donation Services',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="py-16 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Customer Care</h1>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8">At [Your Company Name], we are dedicated to providing exceptional service for blood group detection, blood requests, and blood donations. Our customer care team is here to assist you with any inquiries or support you may need.</p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Blood Group Detection</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">If you have any questions about our fingerprint-based blood group detection system, please reach out to us. Our technology ensures accurate and efficient identification of blood types, making the process swift and reliable.</p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Requesting Blood</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">For assistance with requesting blood, whether for emergencies or scheduled needs, our support team is here to guide you through the process. We are committed to facilitating quick and effective blood requests to meet your needs.</p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Donating Blood</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Interested in donating blood? Our team can provide information on how to get started with blood donation, including eligibility criteria, donation procedures, and how your donation helps save lives.</p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">For any inquiries or support, please contact our customer care team through the following methods:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mb-4">
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@yourcompany.com" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">support@yourcompany.com</a></li>
        <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">+1 (234) 567-890</a></li>
        <li>Address: 123 Health Lane, Suite 456, City, State, ZIP</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg">We strive to respond to all inquiries as promptly as possible. Thank you for choosing [Your Company Name] for your blood care needs.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
